ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, if he/she is interested in graphics.
I would definitely recommend this course to anyone interested in graphics

This course is really helpful for a student who wants to know more about computer graphics since it starts from the very basic concepts and goes through more advanced topics. I would strongly recommend this course to other students.
Good intro graphics course that I am glad I took, but be aware that it was a lot of work.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I'm interested in the field so the course is useful. Helps quite a lot.
This course is really helpful for my research since it helps me grasp the basic knowledge and provide me more space to explore.
